result.name: Kam Fat Restaurant

reviews.text:
Average food for average prices. Fast service. Big portions. English menu. Staff understands some English. They also serve westernized Chinese food.

Updated for family style - the spicy potato beef brisket was really good. Group seating on second floor. Relatively inexpensive. Good service.
Basic eating place with very reasonably priced food. Varied menu with inclusive extras. Definitely a good deal. The food I had was tasty and there was plenty of it.
Good food, inexpensive, but rather comfortable seatings, not uncommon in Hong Kong.
Best milk tea in saiwan
They are good at cooking Beef in Satay Sauce. Their Hong Kong style milk tea is good as well. Suggest to try the Satay Beef Noodle Soup.

result.name: Kam Fat Restaurant 金發茶餐廳

reviews.text:
Average food for average prices. Fast service. Big portions. English menu. Staff understands some English. They also serve westernized Chinese food.

Updated for family style - the spicy potato beef brisket was really good. Group seating on second floor. Relatively inexpensive. Good service.
兩三次都係咁，生米都照俾外賣，其實潷飯時都知㗎啦～照俾就算，返到屋企，全家冇啖好食，當人儍㗎！不幫襯了。
完全垃圾，打電話自己去拎個外賣居然要我係出面等45分鐘，已經吾係第一次，第三次了，完全無改善，員工服務態度差，聽電話果個發緊夢，等左九個字仲要比錯飯我😡
楼上阁楼坐位好有home feel, 食物夠熱，油一D
一般環境,茶餐一間,食材質素尚可以,未達普遍水準?
